Appendix B: Glossary
Term	Definition
Activity	A single step or task in a process
BPMN	Business Process Model and Notation - standard notation
Case	A single instance of a process (e.g., one order)
Conformance	How well actual behavior matches documented process
Event Log	System-generated record of process execution
Fitness	Process mining metric - % of behavior explained by model
Handoff	Transfer of work from one actor/system to another
Swimlane	Visual grouping of activities by role or system
Variant	A unique path through a process
XES	IEEE standard format for event logs